{
  "stem": "19111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- not the Gestapo, but the-- the Wehrmacht was a different-- a different division.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The regular army.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they thought that this was a-- actually that this factory and the people that worked in there, who were actually contributing to the war effort.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so that these are nutzliche Juden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was a nutzliche Jude, which meant he was an important Jew who contributed to the effort by being there and manufacturing the fur vests for the German army.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- got-- just going to tell you-- Vilna had, as I said before, between around 65,000 or 66,000 inhabitants.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right after the-- the yellow stars had to be worn and the walking, the Germans, the Einsatzkommando, that group came in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started rounding up Jews, catching all-- especially males mostly, right from the streets walking, regardless of where, what and how, or what time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just kept scooping them up and taking them to the-- to the city jail, which was on Lukishki.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was called Lukishki Jail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "L-U-K-I-S-H-K-I, I believe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lukishki.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And right from the beginning, the first shot, they rounded up maybe 1,500 or 2,000 Jewish men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took them there and we didn't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- later on, we found out that the town of Ponar, which is, I don't know exactly how many miles away from Vilna, maybe 50 miles or so from Vilna, or 40 miles.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't-- I'm not sure about the mileage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that became the graveyard for the Vilna Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is where 98% of the Vilna Jews were slaughtered over the years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But what they did-- what happened was, we didn't know that anything that has happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
